DATA LICENSING NOTICE:

This project incorporates data from multiple sources with different licenses:

1. EARTHQUAKE DATA (USGS)
   - Source: U.S. Geological Survey Earthquake Hazards Program
   - License: Public Domain
   - URL: https://earthquake.usgs.gov/

2. TECTONIC LINEAMENTS (Myanmar Tectonic Map 2011)
   - Source: Myanmar Geosciences Society
   - License: Open Data

3. BUILDING FOOTPRINTS (GlobalBuildingAtlas)
   - Source: Zhu et al., Technical University of Munich
   - License: CC BY-NC 4.0 (Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0)
   - URL: https://github.com/zhu-xlab/GlobalBuildingAtlas
   - IMPORTANT: Building data is for NON-COMMERCIAL USE ONLY
   
   Citation Required:
   Zhu, X. X., Chen, S., Zhang, F., Shi, Y., and Wang, Y.: GlobalBuildingAtlas: 
   an open global and complete dataset of building polygons, heights and LoD1 3D 
   models, Earth Syst. Sci. Data, 17, 6647â€“6668, 
   https://doi.org/10.5194/essd-17-6647-2025, 2025.

Users of this project must comply with the respective licenses of all data sources.
